  <br/>
  <text class="font-bold">AI Models and Techniques</text>
  <ul class="list-disc md:columns-2 columns-2 mx-6">
    <li>LLMs</li>
    <li>Pre-training, Fine-tuning, Transfer Learning</li>
    <li>High-performance computing (HPC) - Jean-Zay, GPUs</li>
  </ul>
  <br/>
    <text class="font-bold">Operating systems:</text>
    <ul class="list-disc md:columns-4 columns-2 mx-6">
        <li>Unix</li>
        <li>Windows</li>
    </ul>
    <br/>
    <text class="font-bold">Software:</text>
    <ul class="list-disc md:columns-4 columns-2 mx-6">
        <li>Anaconda</li>
        <li>Versioning tools (Git)</li>
        <li>PyCharm</li>
        <li>Microsoft Office Suite</li>
        <li>IntelliJ IDEA</li>
        <li>Android Studio</li>
        <li>Eclipse</li>
        <li>Praat</li>
    </ul>
    <br/>


    <div class="mt-8 mb-5">
        <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Languages</div>
    </div>

    <ul class="list-disc mx-6 mb-10 grid gap-2">
        <li>
            French (Native)
        </li>
        <li>
            English (C1)
        </li>
